Useage:

<labeller type="gitRevisionLabeller">
	<workingDirectory>..\Sources</workingDirectory>
	<incrementOnFailure>False</incrementOnFailure>
</labeller>

The labeller emmits following variables:
$(CCNetGitCommitHash)
$(CCNetGitParentHash)
$(CCNetGitTreeHash)
$(CCNetBuildCycleNumber)
$(CCNetGitRepositoryPath)

It builds the $(CCNetLabel) as follows:
$(CCNetBuildCycleNumber)-GitAbbreviatedCommitHash

The GitAbbreviatedCommitHash is the first seven characters of the $(CCNetGitCommitHash) and is not emmited.



